title: The Atlas of mysterious places.pdf
description:
The Atlas of Mysterious Places - the world's unexplained sacred sites, symbolic landscapes, ancient cities, and lost lands
Weidenfeld & Nicolson | 1987 | 1555841309 | English | 248 pages | PDF | 51 MB

This book is filled with amazing photographs of mysterious places from around the world. Each place is accompained by a wonderful description filled with theories and facts about the place. A guide to many of the world's sacred and mysterious ruins from past civilizations
